IMO, {{champion:127}} lore update feels like a downgrade, she had so much lore with all her monologues.
The Winning HA monologue was removed;
many things were retconned;
her currents quotes don't really reflect her new lore.
But I think it has potential to be something great, let's wait and see what happens.
